data.description: Move in ready home in a great area was built after Katrina.  The home has three floors above flood zone and was built with 2X6 framing with torsion bar strength tied to slab. Dishwasher was upgraded to top of the line. Two primary bedroom walk in closets. Kitchen disposal was recently replaced. Living room, dining room and primary bedroom furniture was bought new a year ago and is available for purchase either in a separate negotiation or as part of the offer. Garage has peg board installed to hang tools.  Large, fenced back yard with access from the driveway.  Two car concrete driveway parking.  Garage door opener and home security system. Large deck at the rear of the home and a deck off the primary bedroom.  Blocks from Buffet Beach, public boat launch and parks.
